data.description: This Free Standing Condo is located in the Worthington Heights complex offering Worthington schools with Columbus taxes. Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and plenty of space for you to entertain or relax in the LL.  The kitchen updates were completed 2020, HVAC 2020, Hot water tank 2020, main floor windows and sliding door 2018, bathrooms updated 2022. and flooring 2020. Outdoor entertainment can be enjoyed on the larger deck and patio. Close to parks, entertainment, shopping.
